<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white> i personally have wielded a exe axe while wearing a fbss and the effects do in fact stack i noticed about a one second drop in delay while axe proc ws in effect.as far as other haste items stack i have no idea but it is a fact that exe axe and fbss do stack<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
